---
// Tidak ada props, hanya pindahan kode section
---
<!-- Alpine.js CDN untuk interaktivitas accordion -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js" defer></script>
<section
  class="relative min-h-screen py-20 flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 to-green-100 overflow-hidden"
  data-aos="fade-up"
>
  <!-- Motif SVG background besar, responsif -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto px-2 z-10 relative" x-data="{ open: 0 }">
    <h2
      class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-center mb-8 text-white drop-shadow-lg flex items-center gap-2"
    >
      <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl">⭐</span> Mengapa Harus Belajar di IniEdu?
    </h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
      <!-- 1 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="0"
      >
        <button
          @click="open === 1 ? open = 0 : open = 1"
          class="w-full flex items-center justify-between py-5 px-3 md:py-6 md:px-6 focus:outline-none"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
            <span class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-cyan-600 mr-2"
              >1.</span
            >
            <span class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800"
              >Belajar dari Mana Saja, Kapan Saja</span
            >
          </div>
          <svg
            :class="{'rotate-90': open === 1}"
            class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-500 transition-transform duration-200"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg
          >
        </button>
        <div
          x-show="open === 1"
          x-transition
          class="px-3 md:px-6 pb-5 text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg"
        >
          Platform online kami bisa diakses fleksibel—cocok untuk guru sibuk,
          pelajar aktif, dan masyarakat umum yang ingin belajar tanpa batas.
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 2 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="100"
      >
        <button
          @click="open === 2 ? open = 0 : open = 2"
          class="w-full flex items-center justify-between py-5 px-3 md:py-6 md:px-6 focus:outline-none"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
            <span class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-cyan-600 mr-2"
              >2.</span
            >
            <span class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800"
              >Materi Berkualitas, Bukan Asal Viral</span
            >
          </div>
          <svg
            :class="{'rotate-90': open === 2}"
            class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-500 transition-transform duration-200"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg
          >
        </button>
        <div
          x-show="open === 2"
          x-transition
          class="px-3 md:px-6 pb-5 text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg"
        >
          Konten dikembangkan oleh pendidik berpengalaman dan pakar industri,
          dengan pendekatan edukatif, aplikatif, dan kontekstual.
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 3 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="200"
      >
        <button
          @click="open === 3 ? open = 0 : open = 3"
          class="w-full flex items-center justify-between py-5 px-3 md:py-6 md:px-6 focus:outline-none"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
            <span class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-cyan-600 mr-2"
              >3.</span
            >
            <span class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800"
              >Sertifikasi Resmi & Profesional</span
            >
          </div>
          <svg
            :class="{'rotate-90': open === 3}"
            class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-500 transition-transform duration-200"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg
          >
        </button>
        <div
          x-show="open === 3"
          x-transition
          class="px-3 md:px-6 pb-5 text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg"
        >
          Setiap program utama dilengkapi dengan sertifikat resmi yang bisa
          digunakan untuk keperluan profesional, CPD, atau pengembangan
          portofolio.
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 4 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="300"
      >
        <button
          @click="open === 4 ? open = 0 : open = 4"
          class="w-full flex items-center justify-between py-5 px-3 md:py-6 md:px-6 focus:outline-none"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
            <span class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-cyan-600 mr-2"
              >4.</span
            >
            <span class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800"
              >Edukasi yang Inklusif & Terjangkau</span
            >
          </div>
          <svg
            :class="{'rotate-90': open === 4}"
            class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-500 transition-transform duration-200"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg
          >
        </button>
        <div
          x-show="open === 4"
          x-transition
          class="px-3 md:px-6 pb-5 text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg"
        >
          Kami ingin semua orang bisa belajar, karena itu program kami disusun
          dengan harga ramah, dan tetap bisa diakses meski dengan koneksi
          terbatas.
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 5 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="400"
      >
        <button
          @click="open === 5 ? open = 0 : open = 5"
          class="w-full flex items-center justify-between py-5 px-3 md:py-6 md:px-6 focus:outline-none"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-5">
            <span class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-cyan-600 mr-2"
              >5.</span
            >
            <span class="font-bold text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800"
              >Fitur Interaktif & Inovatif</span
            >
          </div>
          <svg
            :class="{'rotate-90': open === 5}"
            class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-500 transition-transform duration-200"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg
          >
        </button>
        <div
          x-show="open === 5"
          x-transition
          class="px-3 md:px-6 pb-5 text-gray-700 text-base md:text-lg"
        >
          IniEdu dilengkapi dengan kuis, eBook, latihan, refleksi mandiri, dan
          rekaman kelas untuk belajar lebih fleksibel.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
